443
00:27:48,904 --> 00:27:53,986
Communication is vital to making a game because it requires that people understand

444
00:27:53,986 --> 00:27:58,609
what you're saying so you can collaborate better and be aligned on your goals.

445
00:27:58,609 --> 00:28:01,410
Now, for me, communication also.

446
00:28:02,557 --> 00:28:10,220
includes things like knowing when not to talk and being able to read social cues and also holding

447
00:28:10,220 --> 00:28:15,302
space for others to speak. Okay, and finally, the third one I'm going to talk about here is

